headline: New Union Pacific and Norfolk Southern Intermodal Gateway Expands Market Access
summary: Union Pacific Corporation (NYSE: UNP) and Norfolk Southern Corporation (NYSE: NSC) are launching a new domestic intermodal service to deliver greater market reach and more efficient freight transportation options. The service leverages Union Pacific's premier network to connect customers with key western and southern markets and Norfolk Southern's modernized intermodal facilities in the Louisville area.
